nodes.text: I Hate the Reefs  (and You, Dearest Ex)

"I Hate the Reefs (and You, Dearest Ex)" was a piece of music that was said to have been created by Queen of Echo-Wave. Chass na Chadic owned all of Queen of Echo-Wave's other music, and dismissed "I Hate the Reefs (and You, Dearest Ex)" as an urban legend.
